Package org.apache.calcite.avatica.util

Class AbstractCursor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.calcite.avatica.util.AbstractCursor
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable, Cursor
Direct Known Subclasses:
PositionedCursor
public abstract class AbstractCursor extends Object implements Cursor
Base class for implementing a cursor.

Derived class needs to provide AbstractCursor.Getter and can override Cursor.Accessor implementations if it wishes.
